Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升初中的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都认为自己已经可以独当一面 无所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:02:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜 怒 哀 乐 以为世界上的一切已经无所不知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事实上我们仍然只是被家长和社会保护着的小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的生活中根本不存在真正的悲伤和愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正了解到这点 是我们这十五人集合在一起之后——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第 1 话 游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 还有螃蟹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御友岛的自然原来还有点价值
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都上初中了还到海边来搞什么自然观察
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明显是把我们当小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很适合你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人里只有可奈比较合适
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴 再往前游的话就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可奈好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是小学四年级吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要一个这样的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸红了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可奈一被搂住就会脸红呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逗她啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆在这种地方可是会被海水冲走的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被冲走不正合适么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么非要说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是你亲妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是我 門司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没事 现在正在自由观察呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想把他们也带过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“他们”是…谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么总是没事就欺负可奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看到了 可奈刚才就哭来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇白那家伙又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是一直就那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来谁和谁在一起 到了这里也还是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个学习交流会到底是为了什么的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我倒是觉得跟当初相遇的时候相比 大家的话变得很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一回去马上就去找你 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不等大家一起玩吗 天还没黑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正闲着 有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人有为集体服务的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说个人是为了集体而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 就是说团队合作很重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我踢足球 对这点可是非常了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是正好相反吗 是集体为了个人而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是古茂田议员的女儿 说起这些古板的话可真在行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我古板?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 你爸爸是新闻播音员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是… 往住明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道以后能觉出长得像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名人的女儿可真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你这是干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是别看比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨…讨厌 怎么这么过分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正快死了 有什么所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么干这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想干就干了呗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西 不过是天敌的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区别只在于是被吃掉还是作我的玩物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还不是为了充饥而杀死猪和牛什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那没什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是想得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿自己当圣人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:06:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁放在这的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊 还准备晚上好好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的蛇花也湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是该回宿舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是总觉得好像是没玩够
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也还不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样 大家知道那边有个山洞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山洞?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一说 好像还真听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一眼就看到头了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这个山洞很深
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用全都跟进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探险才最适合暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐变窄了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑黑的看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拽我衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是往回走比较好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是干嘛的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有人住在这呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流浪汉?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点…别扭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 被发现了么…显然是被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么发现的 是看见过我从这里出去过么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本地人都知道这洞 虽然不知道有这么深
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 是这样…原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好你们来了 正合适 你们玩不玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在做游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我在开发过程中获得灵感的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怪人?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不懂礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有十五个敌人要袭击地球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎击它们的是巨大的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的身躯 层层装甲 压倒性的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而操纵它的是——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际是这样 这个游戏马上就要完成了 我正在找试玩的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们正好合适
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常合适
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想参加的人 把手放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结被命运选择的勇者的契约
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别笑 这不是让我不好意思么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情 重要的就是认真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就试试看呗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 顺便告诉我名字 你们的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫和久隆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小高胜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门司邦彦 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫加古功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢村太一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉川宽治
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇白顺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切江洋介
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半井摩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往住爱子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本田千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古茂田孝美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿野万记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町洋子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种…不祥的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 可奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩多好啊 不让她玩太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人怎么!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 十四个人也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都多少岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了可奈大家都是初一 可奈小学四年级
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那个…我叫…你们叫我可可贝利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 可…可可贝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来敌人会接连出现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个由我来打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就轮到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子真奇怪啊 都这么晚了还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们正是贪玩的年龄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都这么黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能大家都一起睡着了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是做梦吧 刚才那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能大家都做一个梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…能看到那个么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就这样…遇到了它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都看不到顶了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有五百米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说有就有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男的说的机器人?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑吧 那不是游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他也说了 是黑色的巨大机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是叫我们去操纵它?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那敌人在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 敌人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说过吧 会有敌人出现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿香 快点去旅馆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你倒是帮帮我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懒得动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地…地震了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晃起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:15:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到驾驶舱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器人里面?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在好好学怎么战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后的战斗我就没法参加了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你做的游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你们一样 不过是游戏中的棋子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 已经过了门限了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是这鬼天气害的 他们该不会出什么事吧 担心死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 仅此而已的话也没办法给对方造成什么伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在动么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要心里想 它就会动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经熟练了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面受到的冲击会经过衰减之后传递进来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶舱本身也被保护在厚重的装甲之下 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 它很强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先用力把装甲剥开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们有再生能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就毁得再彻底些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们有弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体每个敌人弱点的位置并不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大致上都在身体的深处 由很多层装甲保护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到弱点之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就要由你们来保护这个地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:20:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道不是游戏么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人 最后好像要跟我们说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得 似乎是“对不起”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.10,0:23:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这游戏是应该继续还是中止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说希望继续 并不是为了让自己显眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回 Zearth


